(1787, 3, '2018-11-03 03:55:09', '2018-11-03 03:55:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gallery blocks have two settings: the number of columns, and whether or not images should be cropped. The default number of columns is three, and the maximum number of columns is eight.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Below is a three column gallery at full width, with cropped images.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"linkTo\":\"attachment\",\"className\":\"alignfull\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped alignfull\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":611,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"attachment\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"http://localhost/test_wordpress_pocoder/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/canola2/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/test_wordpress_pocoder/wp-content/uploads/2008/06/canola2.jpg\" alt=\"canola\" class=\"wp-image-611\"/></a><figcaption>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Donec mollis. Quisque convallis libero in sapien pharetra tincidunt. Aliquam elit ante, malesuada id, tempor eu, gravida id, odio. Maecenas suscipit, risus et eleifend imperdiet, nisi orci ullamcorper massa, \net adipiscing orci velit quis magna.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":756,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"attachment\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"http://localhost/test_wordpress_pocoder/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/cep00032/\"><img src=\"http://localhost/test_wordpress_pocoder/wp-content/uploads/2008/06/cep00032.jpg\" alt=\"Sunburst Over River\" class=\"wp-image-756\"/></a><figcaption>Sunburst over the Clinch River, \nSouthwest Virginia.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":763,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"attachment\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"http://localhost/test_wordpress_pocoder/2010/09/10/pos